scripts.start-postgres: docker build -t miniprofiler-demo/postgres docker/postgres && docker run -d -p 5444:5432 miniprofiler-demo/postgres
scripts.start-redis: docker build -t miniprofiler-demo/redis docker/redis && docker run -d -p 6379:6379 miniprofiler-demo/redis
scripts.start-services: npm run start-redis && npm run start-postgres
